{"tid":2500284,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"瓏珀山後日第二輪招標，咁啱得咁橋今日一口氣賣出8伙，當然都係招標","createTime":"2021-04-22T13:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:43:47.000Z","uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8319f1d442ab24a60c25be437bdd11787d62584","tid":2500284,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"新地（0016）旗下沙田多石街瓏珀山第一期，本月中首推40伙單位招標，今日（22日）售出8伙，單日吸金逾1.9億元。<br />\n<br />\n據成交紀錄冊顯示，成交單位面積由974至1,502平方呎，屬三、四房間隔，成交價由1,938.88萬至2,905萬元，成交呎價由約1.92萬至2.18萬元。成交價最高的一伙為Crown Tower 17樓A室，面積1,502平方呎，連44平方呎露台及17平方呎工作平台，屬四房，以2,905萬元成交，呎價19,341元。<br />\n<br />\n項目首輪招標涉40伙，招標日期至28日止。早前發展商再加推53伙招標，招標日期由本周六（24日）起至6月30日止。"},{"pid":"640b5730a3c0039afa12ba12b14d8ecb94008cad","tid":2500284,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c65e898522f1a86905a77b9f33b860b48c5f64","tid":2500284,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a